title: What we do hits HOME. Beautiful 2 Bedroom Apt Available Now!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', "ROAD CONTRUCTION SPECIAL: Don't let the road construction detour you, we are open!", 'Apply for your new home the same day you tour & receive $300 OFF a 2 BR or $500 OFF a 3 BR!*', '*Some income and other restrictions may apply.', 'Please call for more details.', 'Offer valid when you apply by 8/5/2022 and move-in by 8/15/2022.', 'Looking to lease a 1, 2, or 3 bedroom apartment home?', 'Albertville Meadows is a well-maintained community located on County Road 37 NE in Albertville.', 'Our community clubhouse, centrally located laundry facilities, and fitness center are all on-site for your convenience.', 'Our professional management team and exceptional customer service ensure your transition into your new home is as smooth as possible.', 'Make sure to stop by the leasing office and say hello.', 'We’d love to welcome you home today!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Private Garages Available - $50/month', '- Utilities Included: Heat, Water, Sewer, Trash', '- Sparkling Outdoor Pool', '- Large Bedrooms With Spacious Closets', '- Standard Kitchen Appliances Included', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'Albertville Meadows Apartments participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380 | 5 Occupants: $76,020 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,660.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:10:30AM-5:00PM', 'Call today to schedule your tour:', 'show contact info', 'Albertville Meadows', '10732 County Road 37 NE', 'Albertville, MN, 55301', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'dc5gQb5yD6u']
